title: Spheric[94]
info:
When i transfered it to my PC, i thought, 'God damn, distorted!' 'Have to capture it new! :p
It's an analog recording with two Effect CPU's in between. I didn't get really how to fix the distortion. But next time, yeah? :)
Spheric[94] is taken from 'Spheric Crap Vol.1' (by flash! :p) and has five components: A SidStation. An 8580 C64 two Effect Gears and a MSSIAH midi Cadridge connected to the Commodore. :-)
